cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) techniques to classify comments against relevant sections of an article. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also involves the development of a deep neural network, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper deals with data-driven commenting systems, which can be categorized under cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
